'''夜曲Op. 27'''是[[蕭邦|蕭邦]]的一組[[夜曲|夜曲]]作品，於1836年創作<ref>{{cite book|last=Huneker|first=James G.|title=Chopin : the man and his music|publisher=Dover Publ.|location=New York|year=1966|page=251|isbn=0-486-21687-X|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=MPFwo8BrkqQC&printsec=titlepage|access-date=2013-05-19|archive-date=2020-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200512032310/https://books.google.com/books?id=MPFwo8BrkqQC&printsec=titlepage|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1837年出版，為兩首互成對比的樂曲。

David Dubal評道：「（這些夜曲）被形容為小型的[[敍事曲|敍事曲]]更為恰當」<ref name="dubal461">{{cite book|last=Dubal|first=David|title=The art of the piano : its performers, literature, and recordings|publisher=Amadeus Press|location=Pompton Plains, N.J.|year=2004|page=461|isbn=1-57467-088-3|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=8698CZGx1ZQC&printsec=frontcover|access-date=2013-08-23|archive-date=2017-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171023152811/https://books.google.com/books?id=8698CZGx1ZQC&printsec=frontcover|dead-url=no}}</ref>；Blair Johnson也指出這兩首曲與[[約翰·菲爾德|約翰·菲爾德]]的夜曲已是幾乎沒有相似之處了<ref name="allmusic">{{cite book |title=AllMusic Guide to Classical Music |last=Woodstra |first=Chris |coauthors=Brennan, Gerald; Schrott, Allen |year=2005 |publisher= Hal Leonard Corporation|isbn= 0-87930-865-6|page= 287 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=n29DHVKhZggC&printsec=frontcover |accessdate=21 March 2009 }}</ref>。

==Op. 27, No. 1==
夜曲Op. 27 No. 1是[[升C小調|升C小調]]，[[速度_(音樂)#基本速度標記|甚緩板]]，4/4拍。在第29[[小節|小節]]轉為樂曲的B段，並註''più mosso''（稍快點），3/4拍，中間一部分為[[降A大調|降A大調]]。第84小節轉回A段，99-101小節以[[慢板|慢板]]作結。
